    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>WELCOME TO BLOOMTHORNE!</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133170/extras/a90098edf8b6076fadb17f9543025db9.poster.avif?t=1767061411\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133170/extras/a90098edf8b6076fadb17f9543025db9.webm?t=1767061411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133170/extras/a90098edf8b6076fadb17f9543025db9.mp4?t=1767061411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the city of <i>Bloomthorne</i>, home of the popular Ball Game! Explore the major locations of this viral hit and challenge many foes all competing to become the Champion of the City! Play as some of the town residents and play through ARCADE MODE to learn about there journey through the Ball Game E-Sports! Or if you want to experience Ball Game at it's highest point fight a local friend in the VERSUS MODE! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>WIDE CAST OF CHARACTERS</strong></u>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133170/extras/153a7eeddd7ea74e9797f30cc9ac7f65.poster.avif?t=1767061411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133170/extras/153a7eeddd7ea74e9797f30cc9ac7f65.webm?t=1767061411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133170/extras/153a7eeddd7ea74e9797f30cc9ac7f65.mp4?t=1767061411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bloomthorne's residents include a group of friends, you are in that group. Choose one of the dorks in this cast of nerds and experience their cool animations and unique supers that should spice up your gameplay from level to level, match to match. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2025 more characters will join this group of individuals allowing you to try out new abilities and techniques to grow your skills in the Ball Games.</p>",
